      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Them did Solomon make to pay tribute.—On them did Solomon levy a tribute. Kings has the fuller expression, mas ‘ôbēd, “tribute of labourers.” “Solomon en fit de levées pour la corvée” (Reuss).",
        "children": [
