      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(9) But of the children of Israel.—See 1Kings 9:22. The Heb. text has the relative (‘asher) after “children of Israel.” But some few MSS., and the ancient versions, omit it. It is, perhaps, an accidental repetition from the beginning of 2Chronicles 8:8.",
