      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Two hundred and fifty.—See 2Chronicles 2:17, and 1Kings 9:23. In the latter place 550 is the number. The number here is an error of transcription, דנ, i.e., 550, having been mistaken for ונ, i.e., 250 (Kennicott).",
